data.description: Contemporary 2019 home w/loads of upgrades. Move right into this 4 BR 2 full Bth home with 2, 261 sq ft under air, oversized 2 car garage, and a stylish open floor plan. Upgrades include impact glass windows & doors, 42-inch soft close kitchen cabinets, upgraded stainless pulls, quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, beautiful wood look flooring throughout which is is 100% waterproof, custom bathroom vanities, upgraded tile in showers, 10 ft ceilings and 8 ft interior doors. Contemporary lighting and plumbing fixtures throughout. The oversized main bedroom features his & hers closets, spacious on-suite bath with double vanities and a huge walk in shower. 3 more spacious bedrooms, 1 with double doors out to the lanai. Large screened in Lanai with TV. New white PVC privacy fence. Garage has a new Belt Driven LiftMaster (quiet) Garage Door Opener with Security Camera that connects directly to your phone or computer. NO HOA
